{"tid":2510691,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"有幾多人曾經比連登/高登仔呃到，以為買樓係無可能？","createTime":"2021-04-30T10:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-30T14:21:51.000Z","uid":52911,"like":28,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"6d7d44ca47da4e8db02c47a6686d4dcb9ce01d77","tid":2510691,"uid":52911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:31:30.000Z","msg":"以前中學雞果陣睇高登 <br />\n成日睇到啲post講咩無父幹無可能買到樓<br />\n或者唔食唔飲幾十年先買得起樓 <br />\n到連登開左仲係間唔中有人講 仲有咩供三十年 供完都60歲<br />\n嗰陣真係覺得買樓係無可能 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n出到社會身邊開始多人買樓 自己先去真正去研究下<br />\n先發現其實唔係想像中咁難 一個正常人實有另一半 一齊儲下錢 大把人30歲前已經買到樓<br />\n而且根本無人真係會供足30年 <br />\n果陣先發現細個自己唔用腦真係比啲報紙佬同兩登啲人洗哂腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家見到啲on9仲係度講咩買樓無可能 有錢人先買到 咩買樓就無人生我實屌鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知有幾多人傻更更比佢地呃撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b663d3d2c81f2476d0b7b8b5b68f2b9b7adda33","tid":2510691,"uid":235637,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:34:17.000Z","msg":"上連登認真個啲人真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c22f94ecf6a386e6ecb0edd02d7e7f98439257f","tid":2510691,"uid":52911,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2b663d3d2c81f2476d0b7b8b5b68f2b9b7adda33","tid":2510691,"uid":235637,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:34:17.000Z","msg":"上連登認真個啲人真係痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:34:59.000Z","msg":"我柒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e8fbd4877c4dcc9fc3691979b4a8a483ef52b14","tid":2510691,"uid":243483,"like":12,"dislike":2,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-30T10:35:25.000Z","msg":"我都係<br />\n洗左咁多年腦<br />\n以為買樓好遙遠<br />\n點知，岩岩30歲就買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申 非專業人士，非父幹"},{"pid":"3d4